{
  "chapter": 100,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙率精兵团前往韩闯行馆，迫使韩闯合作围剿藏匿其中的信陵君手下。韩闯提供暗号\"鲁公多福\"，透露敌方共三十五人由乐刑带领。项少龙设计让韩闯手下先行离开制造动静掩护行动，随后率精兵团潜入行馆后花园。突袭时先掷入风灯照明，使仓内敌人暂时失明，再由上下夹攻以弩箭和近身搏杀全歼敌人，乐刑当场毙命。项少龙从乐刑身上搜回《鲁公秘录》正本和手抄本。事后在孝成王面前汇报，郭开质疑不留活口的决策，项少龙以保护秘录为由解释，晶王后帮腔证实敌方身份。孝成龙颜大悦予以嘉赏，项少龙趁机请求增强城防获准。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "侯爷合作还是不合作？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你说怎样就怎样吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "嘱你的手下全体出来协助搜捕贼人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们全部给本侯出来，好助城守追捕贼党。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下马！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "着你的手下们直奔过去，一切均须听我的人吩咐！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "侯爷，现在整个区域均给我们重重包围，没有人可闯进这几条街的范围里，只要侯爷肯与我们合作，我可说是敌人埋伏在雅夫人府后园处，准备行刺雅夫人，给我们逐出来，避往侯爷行馆的方向去，侯爷以为这计划行得通吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可以不留下任何活口吗？里面尚有十多名婢仆。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "那些婢仆知情吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "要看情况而定，胡乱杀人，反会使人起疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一切由你们作主吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "部署妥当了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他们共有三十五个人，不过人人身手高强，带头者是乐刑，乃信陵君的得力手下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "你们的人若要进入他们躲身后院的那座粮仓，是否须什么暗号？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "暗号是'鲁公多福'，记着不留一人，赵雅处亦烦请董兄装模作样一番。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "侯爷放心，在此事上我董匡定与侯爷共进退，事后那些尸体会广布在后院、墙头和街上，何况孝成王只要得回《秘录》，哪还计较是怎样得回来的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "最怕你下面的人会泄出秘密。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "封锁外围的是本地的赵兵，但参与行动的全是随我来的族人。打从开始知道此事与侯爷有关，我便立下决心不顾一切为侯爷掩饰。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄确够朋友！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "侯爷请移驾与贵仆们会合，等待消息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鲁公多福！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仓内守卫",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "什么事？这时怎可来找我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快开门！侯爷着我们来有要事相告。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你真要为韩闯掩饰吗？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "我是否太心软呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "时间无多，我们快布置吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董将军为何如此失策，竟不留下任何活口，好向信陵君兴问罪之师？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "text": "若安厘得到这批人证，说不定可整治魏无忌，看来偷袭龙阳君者，亦必有这批人的份儿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "郭大夫言之有理，董将军有什么话说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "text": "鄙人是别无选择，必须尽速痛下杀手，否则若教对方自知难以幸免而毁去《鲁公秘录》，纵使只是毁去部分，我们也得不偿失。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wang_hou",
      "speaker_name": "晶王后",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "text": "龙阳君认出其中几个人来，更证实带头者乃信陵君的食客乐刑，只要把尸体全部送返大梁，我看无忌公子会非常烦恼呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董卿立此大功，寡人自当有赏，唔……",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "text": "大王愧煞鄙人了，鄙人让这群凶徒潜伏邯郸而不察，终是玩忽职守，大王不予计较，已是最大的恩典。鄙人提议把这些人示众三天，公告全城，好安国民之心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "text": "为城防安全，鄙人想调动人马增强城防，望大王钦准。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_cheng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "孝成王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "卿家快把计划递上来让寡人一看，若无问题，立即批准。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 100,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    }
  ],
